      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V pedigree; release version controlled; solver regression tests passing for hemolysis-relevant benchmarks.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 used under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Solver regression suite executed at project initiation; all 47 benchmark cases passed. Version locked in configuration management record CM-2024-003."
