      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence study with GCI < 5 % on QoI (hemolysis index and pressure head) for production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation study performed: coarse 1.8 M, medium 4.2 M, fine 9.1 M cells. GCI for hemolysis index: 2.1 % (medium-to-fine). Production mesh selected at 4.2 M cells balancing accuracy and throughput. y+ < 1 maintained on all wetted surfaces."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
