      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; analyst qualifications and simulation protocol review considered sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Simulation analysts hold ANSYS Fluent certification and minimum 5 years turbomachinery CFD experience. Simulation protocol reviewed by independent senior analyst prior to production runs. Formal use-error assessment not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Governing equations and turbulence closure appropriate for rotating internal flow at Reynolds numbers encountered in CPB pump operation; model form justified by literature.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating passage flows (Re 10,000–80,000). Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model adopted per FDA guidance. Multiple reference frame approach for impeller-volute interaction validated in literature."
    },
