      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model inputs (geometry, boundary conditions, material properties) traceable to measurements or authoritative sources with stated uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Pump geometry from FDA-published CAD file (version 1.3). Fluid properties from NIST database at 37 °C. Rotational speed and flow rates from experimental protocol with stated uncertainties (±0.5 % RPM, ±1 % flow). Input traceability matrix documented in model input report MIR-2024-CPB."
    },
